#! Languages

 <!--hvy:text {}-->
  # Languages

 <!--hvy:component-list {"css":"margin: 0;","tags":"language","componentListComponent":"language-record","componentListItemLabel":"language"}-->
<!--hvy: {"id":"section-pki90b","lock":true,"expanded":true,"highlight":false,"tags":"reciprocal-xref-source","description":"Work history","hideIfUnmodified":true}-->
#! Professional History

 <!--hvy:text {}-->
  # Professional History

 <!--hvy:table {"lock":true,"css":"margin: 0.5rem 0 0;","tags":"table-header","description":"History table header","tableColumns":["TITLE","<!--hvy:alt {\"compact\":\"ORG\"}-->ORGANIZATION<!--/hvy:alt-->","YEAR(S)"]}-->

 <!--hvy:component-list {"id":"history-list","css":"margin: 0;","tags":"history","componentListComponent":"history-record","componentListItemLabel":"job"}-->
  <!--hvy:component-list:0 {}-->

   <!--hvy:history-record {"id":"senior-software-engineer-ii"}-->
    <!--hvy:expandable:stub {}-->

     <!--hvy:table {"css":"margin: 0; margin-top: -1px;","tableColumns":["TITLE","<!--hvy:alt {\"compact\":\"ORG\"}-->ORGANIZATION<!--/hvy:alt-->","YEAR(S)"],"tableShowHeader":false,"tableRows":[{"cells":["Senior Software Engineer II","Carta","2020-2023"]}]}-->

    <!--hvy:expandable:content {"css":"padding: 0.5rem;"}-->

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0 0 0.35rem;","placeholder":"Organization"}-->
      Carta

     <!--hvy:grid {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;"}-->
      <!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"history-location"}-->

       <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;","placeholder":"location"}-->
        Seattle, WA

      <!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"history-date-range"}-->

       <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0; text-align: right;","placeholder":"date range"}-->
        May 2020 – Jan 2023

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0; font-weight: 700;","placeholder":"job title"}-->
      Senior Software Engineer II

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;","placeholder":"description"}-->
      Worked primarily in Python with some JavaScript/TypeScript front-end development; decomposed an existing feature out of the monolith, created a Plaid integration, created a CLI application for developers, and worked on CI improvements. Led design and implemented components for an automated money movement project spanning three services and a third-party vendor. Surveyed developers, analyzed pain points, and improved developer experience and velocity by creating and maintaining developer containers, evangelizing and training on developer containers and DevSpace, bringing Github Codespaces to Carta, and communicating cross-team about developer pain points.

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
      ^section-heading^ #### Accomplishments

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;","placeholder":"accomplishments"}-->
      Won the December 2022 hackathon with a hot reloading Python test server/daemon
      Added a database migration linter to the main monolith
      Created a gRPC permission system for the investor services team
      Wrote the backend portion of Investor Service’s Plaid integration
      Created an in-depth self-guided bootcamp for DevSpace
      Wrote most of a developer CLI application
      Created and maintained the core monolith developer container

     <!--hvy:skills-and-tools-tech-list {}-->
      <!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"relevant-skills"}-->

       <!--hvy:container {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
        <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
         ^panel-heading^ #### Relevant Skills

        <!--hvy:component-list {"css":"margin: 0;","componentListComponent":"skill-xref-card","componentListItemLabel":"skill reference"}-->

      <!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"tools-technologies"}-->

       <!--hvy:container {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
        <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
         ^panel-heading^ #### Tools and Technologies

        <!--hvy:component-list {"css":"margin: 0;","componentListComponent":"tool-tech-xref-card","componentListItemLabel":"tool / tech reference"}-->

  <!--hvy:component-list:1 {}-->

   <!--hvy:history-record {"id":"senior-backend-engineer-lead-backend-engineer"}-->
    <!--hvy:expandable:stub {}-->

     <!--hvy:table {"css":"margin: 0; margin-top: -1px;","tableColumns":["TITLE","<!--hvy:alt {\"compact\":\"ORG\"}-->ORGANIZATION<!--/hvy:alt-->","YEAR(S)"],"tableShowHeader":false,"tableRows":[{"cells":["Senior Backend Engineer / Lead Backend Engineer","Premise Data","2017-2020"]}]}-->

    <!--hvy:expandable:content {"css":"padding: 0.5rem;"}-->

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0 0 0.35rem;","placeholder":"Organization"}-->
      Premise Data

     <!--hvy:grid {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;"}-->
      <!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"history-location"}-->

       <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;","placeholder":"location"}-->
        Seattle, WA

      <!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"history-date-range"}-->

       <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0; text-align: right;","placeholder":"date range"}-->
        Nov 2017 – Feb 2020

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0; font-weight: 700;","placeholder":"job title"}-->
      Senior Backend Engineer / Lead Backend Engineer

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;","placeholder":"description"}-->
      Developed and maintained App Engine services in Python, Scala, and Java; led design of new features, coached team members, investigated and fixed production issues, provided support across teams, documented existing systems, developed dataflow pipelines, did occasional front-end updates with ReactJS, and ran productive meetings and coached on Scrum.

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
      ^section-heading^ #### Accomplishments

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;","placeholder":"accomplishments"}-->
      Won the Premise Impact Award in Q4 2018
      Improved backend and front-end while understaffed
      Improved task reservation system performance and reduced datastore costs
      Led design and implementation of a visualization service
      Established a system for managing and prioritizing tech debt, bugs, and developer issues
      Identified inefficient BigQuery queries in a Periscope dashboard

     <!--hvy:skills-and-tools-tech-list {}-->
      <!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"relevant-skills"}-->

       <!--hvy:container {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
        <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
         ^panel-heading^ #### Relevant Skills

        <!--hvy:component-list {"css":"margin: 0;","componentListComponent":"skill-xref-card","componentListItemLabel":"skill reference"}-->

      <!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"tools-technologies"}-->

       <!--hvy:container {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
        <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
         ^panel-heading^ #### Tools and Technologies

        <!--hvy:component-list {"css":"margin: 0;","componentListComponent":"tool-tech-xref-card","componentListItemLabel":"tool / tech reference"}-->

  <!--hvy:component-list:2 {}-->

   <!--hvy:history-record {"id":"senior-software-engineer"}-->
    <!--hvy:expandable:stub {}-->

     <!--hvy:table {"css":"margin: 0; margin-top: -1px;","tableColumns":["TITLE","<!--hvy:alt {\"compact\":\"ORG\"}-->ORGANIZATION<!--/hvy:alt-->","YEAR(S)"],"tableShowHeader":false,"tableRows":[{"cells":["Senior Software Engineer","Zonar Systems","2015-2017"]}]}-->

    <!--hvy:expandable:content {"css":"padding: 0.5rem;"}-->

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0 0 0.35rem;","placeholder":"Organization"}-->
      Zonar Systems

     <!--hvy:grid {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;"}-->
      <!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"history-location"}-->

       <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;","placeholder":"location"}-->
        Seattle, WA

      <!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"history-date-range"}-->

       <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0; text-align: right;","placeholder":"date range"}-->
        June 2015 – Sept 2017

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0; font-weight: 700;","placeholder":"job title"}-->
      Senior Software Engineer

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;","placeholder":"description"}-->
      Worked on the data services team building a customer-facing access API using SQLAlchemy ORM in Python, including column selection and custom queries, and ported/improved reports based on complex database sprocs; later led the OEM microservices team, mentored team members, improved team velocity, and designed/developed the code base for Google App Engine.

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
      ^section-heading^ #### Accomplishments

     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;","placeholder":"accomplishments"}-->
      Improved bulk uploads for ZPass users
      Improved query/report speed
      Developed a large portion of the data service for the customer-facing front-end application
      Designed column selection and query support
      Ported and improved reports
      Defined better test practices and a microservice test plan

     <!--hvy:skills-and-tools-tech-list {}-->
      <!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"relevant-skills"}-->

       <!--hvy:container {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
        <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
         ^panel-heading^ #### Relevant Skills

        <!--hvy:component-list {"css":"margin: 0;","componentListComponent":"skill-xref-card","componentListItemLabel":"skill reference"}-->

      <!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"tools-technologies"}-->

       <!--hvy:container {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
